NNEWI – Most Rev.Daddy Hezekiah, the founder and leader of the Living Christ .Mssion In­corporated, has admonished Nigerians to thank God for protection in this year 2020 which was characterized by scourge of Covid19. Giving this admonition in his Christmas message released in his church head­quaters in Onitsha, Anambra State, on Thursday, Hezekiah noted that Nigerians should always be grateful to God, adding that despite the dev­astating effect of the disease, God was able to protect them. On Christmas celebra­tion,he stated that the people should celebrate it by empha­sizing on holy living which glorifies God, adding that people should shuns vices like womanizing, drunken­ness, high profiteering,etc which don’t please God. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Said he, “Many people misinterpret Christmas to be only a period of merriment, gifts sharing,as well as par­tying, Christmas symbolizes God’s love and salvation to humanity, so the celebration will be anchored on righ­teousness,my appeal to ev­erybody who survivied this year which is perilous they should celebrate this special Christmas wisely and give God due respect and honour.” SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION